Fortnite is an online video game developed by Epic Games and relin 2017. It is available
in three distinct game mode versions that otherwise share thegeneral gameplay and game
engine: Fortnite Battle Royale, a free-to-play battle royale gawhich up to 100 players
fight to be the last person standing; Fortnite: Save the Worcooperative hybrid tower
defense-shooter and survival game in which up to four players fighzombie-like creatures
and defend objects with traps and fortifications they can buildFortnite Creative, in which
players are given complete freedom to create worlds and battle arenas.